Reluctance
Piece 1 of 4 of the Becoming NFT image series 
Reluctance - Resistance - Endurance - Acceptance

What will become of us and our art?
"Becoming NFT" is a unique artwork series created in Virtual Reality addressing the transformation of our art and questions the effect on our daily lives as we fade into the blockchain...
